review.reviewBody: Really enjoyed the 46. Beef with Green Pepper & Black Bean Sauce, and the restaurant accommodated special instructions.  Will order again
Wo's never disappoints! And they always take care as well as accommodate requests!
The Snap Peas with Beef was very nicely prepared. The beef was delightfully tender; and there were lots of good crisp veggies. All in all, a healthy dish.
Favourite spot for noodles, always get 121. Chicken Chow Mein (Soft Noodle) and 127. Singapore Style Fried Vermicelli, always so good!
The crispy tofu is so good!  Also the chicken chow mein & spring rolls, will definitely order again!  Even my little boy loves everything from here :)
